34:15.600 --> 34:17.533
Please get someone to help me.

34:18.233 --> 34:19.800
I'm here to help you.

34:19.866 --> 34:22.000
What's the matter,
aren't I good enough for you?

34:22.066 --> 34:23.366
No, it's not that, it's--

34:23.433 --> 34:24.766
No, no, I get it.

