35:26.600 --> 35:28.533
You'll be fine.

35:44.400 --> 35:46.333
You're making me crazy.

35:48.233 --> 35:49.300
'Karyn?'

36:38.966 --> 36:39.933
'Karyn?'

36:42.700 --> 36:43.700
Bryan?

36:54.966 --> 36:56.733
Shh!

36:57.366 --> 36:58.633
Come on.

