That's how you do it.

37:43.700 --> 37:46.733
Yeah, yeah.
Take it in your hand.

37:46.800 --> 37:48.266
- Oh.
- Come on.

37:48.333 --> 37:51.266
I'm so.. I don't know
that I shouldn't..

37:51.333 --> 37:53.300
- 'I told you not to be afraid.'
- 'Okay.'

37:55.733 --> 37:57.700
Don't be afraid. It's the only
way you're gonna learn.

37:58.933 --> 38:00.666
- There you go.
- Ooh!

38:00.733 --> 38:02.433
- This is fun.
- Beautiful.

38:03.800 --> 38:05.966
- Tie.
- Is that good? Is that good?

38:06.033 --> 38:07.433
Yes.

38:09.700 --> 38:11.433
- 'Over and under.'
- 'Mm-hmm.'

