38:14.700 --> 38:16.833
- Oh.
- Damn, look what I did.

38:18.666 --> 38:20.600
Up. I've seen worse.

38:20.666 --> 38:22.800
Do it this way.
We'll go underneath.

38:24.800 --> 38:26.133
There we go.

38:33.866 --> 38:35.833
Yes, practice makes perfect.

38:38.400 --> 38:40.633
What if she has
to tell us something?

38:40.700 --> 38:44.133
Oh...you'll be fine.

38:44.200 --> 38:46.700
Yeah. You'll be okay.

39:23.633 --> 39:25.200
Uh! Now, now.

39:25.266 --> 39:27.800
We mustn't bother
poor Mr. Shrek.

39:27.866 --> 39:30.000
- What's wrong with him?
- You don't wanna know.

39:30.066 --> 39:32.166
And besides you've got
other things to think about.

39:32.233 --> 39:33.600
Your parents are gonna
be here soon.

39:33.666 --> 39:34.933
Can't you get it
through your heads

39:35.000 --> 39:37.500
my parents are not coming.

39:37.566 --> 39:40.133
Don't you understand anything?

39:40.200 --> 39:42.100
No, no more drugs.

39:42.166 --> 39:44.833
Don't worry,
I've never missed yet.

39:50.300 --> 39:52.733
Wow! Made the fame.
Way to go.

41:10.866 --> 41:12.700
I'm not Shrek..

41:28.000 --> 41:29.233
Bryan?

41:45.433 --> 41:47.033
Bryan?

41:57.633 --> 41:59.833
No!

42:12.533 --> 42:15.833
No! No! No!

42:15.900 --> 42:18.800
No! No! No!

42:31.066 --> 42:32.200
Ah!

42:33.833 --> 42:36.166
Practice makes perfect.

42:36.233 --> 42:38.233
Come on in.

42:38.300 --> 42:39.700
